{"tid":1106100,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"極火蝦離奇消失","createTime":"2019-04-14T11:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T11:41:51.000Z","uid":5704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3b8bdd4c7470723c76e19f09154258ec4596ffde","tid":1106100,"uid":5704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:05:55.000Z","msg":"每次養觀賞蝦都養得唔長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間唔中就會有啲空殻出現<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DFfciPe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDFfciPe.png&h=a4ac7398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為以前有過渦蟲出現<br />\n諗住個原因會係渦蟲<br />\n所以翻過缸<br />\n雖然之後起碼沙上面嘅地方都冇再見過<br />\n但都keep住有空殻出現<br />\n就諗會唔會係關一齊養嘅新燈事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vOp1cay.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvOp1cay.png&h=af0ab5ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁我諗個缸應該有好多地方可以避開啲燈<br />\n因為都算係雜草叢生<br />\n當然我都少換水<br />\n依家諗緊個主要原因會係咩<br />\n<br />\n背景: 18吋缸，生物環濾桶，24℃水冷"},{"pid":"2d421370f4af9e1905658d3513fa898d5c94415b","tid":1106100,"uid":93410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:34:02.000Z","msg":"魚係會食蝦<br />\n<br />\n利申：養咗魚十幾年"},{"pid":"4a32546e67a10e7d12ae8a057df20caa5814bb64","tid":1106100,"uid":51388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:41:51.000Z","msg":"魚會食蝦，蝦會換殼失敗死，好多原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}